title: Belgium: Thousands join Puigdemont in Brussels rally for Catalan independence
description:
Tens of thousands of Catalans descended on the streets of the Belgian capital of Brussels on Thursday to march in support of the Catalan independence.

Former Catalan President Carles Puigdemont, who is currently in self-imposed exile in Belgium, joined protesters in Brussels to demand the backing of EU institutions for the separatist cause.
